The hours for the University of Michigan Intramural Sports Building can vary depending on the day of the week and time of year. Typically, the building is open Monday through Friday from 6:00am to midnight, Saturday from 8:00am to 10:00pm, and Sunday from 10:00am to midnight during the academic year. However, it is important to note that these hours are subject to change during holidays, academic breaks, and summer months. It is recommended to check the Intramural Sports Building website or contact them directly for the most up-to-date information on their hours of operation.